  <sys:String x:Key="StringSerialTranslationMsg2">Note that openMenu has always performed these serial translations automatically, regardless of user settings. As a result, artwork lookups and the IDs used for virtual VMU devices expect the adjusted versions of these serials.</sys:String>
  <sys:String x:Key="StringSerialTranslationMsg3">It's highly recommended you allow these serials to also be translated here in GD MENU Card Manager for compatibility with artwork lookups and virtual VMU devices.</sys:String>
